      "id": "PopularPost107184",
      "post_content": "Excellent card for Red Deck Wins and Land Destruction type decks. It forces your opponents to make difficult decisions right from the get-go. Also note the subtle difference between a card that says \"When ~this~ is put in the graveyard, ...\" and \"Sacrifice ~this~: ...\" -- This card stayed good even after the removal of stacked combat damage. Might have even been playable in Extended if Extended had stayed \"big\".",
      "posted_by": "bif",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost107184\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Excellent card for Red Deck Wins and Land Destruction type decks.  It forces your opponents to make difficult decisions right from the get-go.  Also note the subtle difference between a card that says \"When ~this~ is put in the graveyard, ...\" and \"Sacrifice ~this~: ...\" -- This card stayed good even after the removal of stacked combat damage.  Might have even been playable in Extended if Extended had stayed \"big\".</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '107184'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy45489\">bif</span>\r\n                                (10/1/2010 11:07:05 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png